precis:
Amendments to the PACIFIC PILOTAGE TARIFF REGULATIONS which increase the
tariff rates in all compulsory pilotage areas by 1.5% as well the travel-
related rates, and introduce a new port-to-port fee of $360 per assignment,
effective February 1, 1996.
